| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1037 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 810b291c-52a2-537b-9b0f-abe97dbb7a4d"
